{"tid":1527361,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發][正視聽]香港機場並沒有暫停飛機降落","createTime":"2019-09-01T10:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T11:49:31.000Z","uid":219955,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"406a888549979d4adcf1bbc3153914f794c16814","tid":1527361,"uid":219955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T10:00:44.000Z","msg":"Hi 各位手足又係我<br />\n出面好多風吹緊話停飛要走<br />\n我可以話比大家聽<span style=\"color: red;\">依家絕對冇停飛</span><br />\n香港機場係進行緊flow control (即係平時好熟悉嘅人流管制)<br />\n<a href=\"https://pilotweb.nas.faa.gov/PilotWeb/notamRetrievalByICAOAction.do?method=displayByICAOs&amp;reportType=RAW&amp;formatType=DOMESTIC&amp;retrieveLocId=VHHH&amp;actionType=notamRetrievalByICAOs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpilotweb.nas.faa.gov%2FPilotWeb%2FnotamRetrievalByICAOAction.do%3Fmethod%3DdisplayByICAOs%26reportType%3DRAW%26formatType%3DDOMESTIC%26retrieveLocId%3DVHHH%26actionType%3DnotamRetrievalByICAOs&d=I3kI68XCunzd%2BKkpJ1XxGPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=31c66ba4\" target=\"_blank\">https://pilotweb.nas.faa.gov/PilotWeb/notamRetrievalByICAOAction.do?method=displayByICAOs&amp;reportType=RAW&amp;formatType=DOMESTIC&amp;retrieveLocId=VHHH&amp;actionType=notamRetrievalByICAOs</a><br />\n<blockquote>E) DUE TO ATFM MEASURE, FLOW CONTROL RESTRICTIONS IMPOSED FOR <br />\nTRAFFIC <br />\nLANDING HONG KONG INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT AS FOLLOWS:<br />\n<br />\nDEP FROM AIRPORTS WITHIN FUKUOKA AND INCHEON FIR:<br />\n<br />\nVIA BULAN A1 - 15 MINUTES <br />\nVIA IGURU G581 - 15 MINUTES <br />\nVIA SALMI A1 - 35 MINUTES <br />\n<br />\nRMK: FLOW CONTROL MAY BE ADJUSTED SUBJECT TO SITUATION AND <br />\nDISCRETION OF HONG KONG ATS WATCH SUPERVISOR.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係叫人散水定留<br />\n係俾多啲資訊前線決定<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"3f3e2e88ab753fde5c969b6fbda50fe1962046bc","tid":1527361,"uid":219955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"reply